Cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta kara yaduwa a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Bayanan da ke tattare da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna cewa duk da cewa annobar ta COVID-19 tana da matakai daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, duk da haka tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar cutar a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da ɗakunan kulawa na musamman dole ne su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don babban raƙuman marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci sabis na kiwon lafiya na musamman, musamman kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2020, an bayar da rahoton wani gungu na masu fama da cutar huhu da ba a san dalilin ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa cutar, wacce ke da sabon nau'in coronavirus, daga yanzu za a kira ta da cutar coronavirus-2 mai saurin numfashi mai tsanani, ko kuma SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira shi cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai da ake da su zuwa yanzu sun nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19 suna fuskantar cutar a cikin ƙananan cututtukan numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan ƙwayoyin suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na masu cutar, COVID-19 ya zama mafi tsanani wanda ya sa marasa lafiya suka shiga asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na masu cutar da suka kamu da cutar suka shiga kulawa ta musamman.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke kwance a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yaduwar cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya kuma mun kwatanta yanayin da lardin Hubei na China.
Har ila yau, muna kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Ingila tare da waɗanda ke da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila
Bayan haka, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu yankuna na duniya, kuma yanayin cutar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya yanzu yana bin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Sakatare Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana annobar COVID-19.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na mujallar Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbataccen yanayin cutar ta COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an ba da rahoton farkon waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a Faransa a tsakanin matafiya da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duk kasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya (UK), inda aka samu mutum 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutum 1,727 da suka mutu a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da Italiya kadai da mutum 1,7750 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutum 1,441 da suka mutu.
Samun adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma bayyanarsu
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana samun bayanan mutanen da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a kowace rana daga tushen hukuma kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki a waɗannan ƙasashe da WHO kuma ana sabunta su da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da bayanan ne don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Ingila da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin tushen tantance yaduwar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa gajerun kwanaki 14 na cutar COVID-19, don haka an yi la'akari da lokacin COVID-19 na yau da kullun, a kowace EU / EEA da Burtaniya, a cikin lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
An kuma gwada adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa da aka samu a karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga watan Maris na 2020 da na 31 ga watan Janairu zuwa 15 ga watan Maris na 2020.
Yanayin kamuwa da COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila
Yanayin da aka lura a cikin gajeren kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya ya yi daidai da yanayin da aka nuna a lardin Hubei na China (Hoto 1).
Gabaɗaya, a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya, tarin COVID-19 ya fara kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya fara ƙaruwa cikin sauri kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (abubuwan da aka haɗe).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar adadin wadanda aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan ƙaruwar yanayin a cikin tarin COVID-19 (buƙatar da aka haɗe).
Hoto na 2 ya kwatanta adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila da kuma wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya bayyana cewa zuwa karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga watan Maris, wasu kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Ingila sun bayar da rahoton adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar, wanda ya yi daidai da na Italiya a makonni 3 da suka gabata ko kasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin tabbataccen masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri.
Hanyoyin da aka lura da su a cikin tarin COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar ta yadu a cikin ƙasa iri ɗaya.
Duk da cewa kasashe suna fuskantar matakai daban-daban na barkewar cutar, akwai bambance-bambance game da yadda hukumomin kiwon lafiyar jama'a na kasashe ke amsawa, kuma a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, ana amfani da ƙa'idodi daban-daban ga mutanen da ke buƙatar yin gwajin tabbatarwa ko ƙarin gwajin COVID-19.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke da ciwon daji a Italiya sun ba da rahoton yanayin da kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa an riga an cika iyakar ƙarfin asibitoci da sassan kulawa ta musamman a waɗannan yankuna.
A halin yanzu, a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA, kawai a cikin kashi 6% da 1% na masu haƙuri na COVID-19 suna da bayanai game da asibiti da / ko shiga kulawa ta musamman (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Koyaya, dole ne a tattara su ta hanyar da ta dace don amfani da su azaman ƙarin bayanan sa ido na yanzu, da kuma mai da hankali kan adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito da kuma mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a 11-2010 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin samun damar asibitocin kulawa ta musamman da na matsakaici a Turai, wanda ya bambanta daga asibitoci 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal a kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa waɗannan ƙasashe suna da albarkatu da yawa ko ƙasa da Italiya (ƙimar matsakaicin gado 12.5 na kulawa ta musamman a kowace mutane 100,000 a cikin 2010-11).
An gabatar da yanayin samfurin da ya danganci wadatar lafiyar lafiya da magani tare da kimantawa ga kowace EU / EEA memba da Burtaniya dangane da yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke da haɗarin > 90% na wucewar ƙarfin asibitocin kulawa ta musamman a cikin na shida na ECDC na saurin kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Tunda an riga an gano cututtukan da ke da cutar a wasu yankuna a cikin EU / EEA da Ingila, kuma asibitoci da asibitocin kulawa ta musamman galibi suna ba da sabis ga yawan jama'a na yanki, ya kamata a ba da bayanai game da cututtukan da ke da cutar da kuma asibitocin kulawa ta musamman bisa ga tsarin yanki na yanki don matakin kididdiga na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar cutar a Italiya da yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da kuma sassan kulawa ta musamman su shirya kansu don fuskantar yanayin watsawa na SARS-CoV-2 mai ci gaba da yawa kuma su samar da shirye-shirye don karɓar marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19, musamman a cikin kulawa ta musamman, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da ke yankin Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon kimanta haɗarin ECDC, don jinkirta yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 zuwa hanzari, gaba ɗaya da kuma sauya yanayin daga ƙuntatawa zuwa rage saurin annoba, ya zama dole, saboda idan ba a ɗauki matakan da suka dace ba, saurin karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar da ake tsammani na iya ba wa hukumomin yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen damar ganowa, karɓa da aiwatar da martani mai dacewa.
