Idan ba haka ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA na iya fuskantar babban ɗumbin marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
