A matsayin cutar da ke fitowa, COVID-19 kwanan nan ya fara nuna ƙarin lokacin asibiti a cikin dubban marasa lafiya.
A mafi yawan lokuta, marasa lafiya suna samun sauƙi a hankali kuma ba tare da wani rikitarwa ba.
