Tushen dabbobi na kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum
Shekaru dubbai, canji da daidaitawa sun taimaka wajen juyin halitta na coronavirus (CoVs) da kuma masu masaukin su, gami da mutane.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa kwayar cutar korona ta mutum (HCoV) biyu tana haifar da cututtuka masu saurin gaske, kamar su cutar zazzabin cizon sauro.
An nuna barkewar cutar SARS da cutar MERS a kan wasu tsabar kudi, wanda ke nuna yadda cutar ta cutar coronavirus ta mutum ke iya cutarwa da kuma hadari.
Bayyanar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019, ya sake sanya coronavirus a cikin hankali kuma ya ba mu mamaki tare da iyawar watsawa mai tsawo, amma ba shi da cutarwa idan aka kwatanta da ɗan'uwansa SARS-CoV.
Cutar kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar ta mutum tana da asalin dabba (zoonosis), kuma sanin asalin kwayar cutar ta mutum zai iya taimaka mana sosai.
Yawancin kwayar cutar ta mutum ta samo asali ne daga batsa, wadanda ba su da cutar.
An kuma san wasu kwayar cutar ta HCoVs a matsayin majiyar matsakaiciyar tanki.
Gano dabbobi masu masaukin baki yana taimakawa kai tsaye wajen hana kamuwa da cutar a cikin mutane.
Binciken hulɗar mai watsa labaran coronavirus a cikin dabbobi na iya ba da mahimman bayanai game da cutar a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, muna ba da cikakken bayani game da bayanan da ke akwai game da kwayar cutar HCoVs guda bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da kuma asalin dabbobi da watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Mafi mahimmanci, muna kwatanta da kuma magance nau'ikan kwayar cutar ta mutum daban-daban daga yanayin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar da kuma tsarin kwayar halitta.
Ana tattauna cutar ta COVID-19 ta yanzu a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da ƙari, yanayin da ake buƙata don nasarar motsawa tsakanin masu masaukin baki da kuma bayyanar cututtukan cutar da ke faruwa a cikin cutar ta zama abin lura.
