Dukkan nau'ikan kwayar cutar ta mutum guda bakwai sun samo asali ne daga dabbobi daga batsa, beraye da dabbobi masu gida.
Shaida mai yawa ta tabbatar da cewa asalin juyin halitta na dukkan kwayar cutar ta mutum shine batsa, inda ƙwayoyin cuta ke daidaitawa sosai amma ba su da cutarwa kuma suna da bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta haifar da manyan kalubale na likita, kimiyya, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a ga China da duniya.
Binciken asalin dabbobi na HCoVs yana ba da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, ƙarfin motsawa da abubuwan da ke iyakance bambancin bambancin.
Hakanan yana iya sauƙaƙe ko jagorantar bincike game da dabbobi masu ajiya, matsakaici, da masu haɓaka SARS-CoV-2 kuma ana iya amfani da su don hana irin waɗannan abubuwan a nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bita na nazarin, muna ba da cikakken bayani game da asalin dabbobi, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna, da kuma aikin cututtukan HCoVs.
Musamman, muna nunawa da kuma tattauna yanayin da ya saba cewa kwayar cutar mahaifa ta HCoVs ba ta da cutar a cikin rukunin masu masaukin su, amma ta zama mai cutar bayan yaduwar tsakanin nau'ikan zuwa sabon mai masaukin.
Muna kuma nazarin yanayin juyin halittar kwayar cutar ta HCoV, inda yawanci haɓakar watsawa ke tare da raguwar aikin cutar.
