Karfafawa da tallafawa wanke hannu da sabulu na iya tasiri kan yanke shawara, fadakar da jama'a game da fa'idodin wanke hannu, da kuma haifar da sauya halaye na dogon lokaci a cikin al'umma.
Don ingantaccen aiki, kulawa da kimantawa suna da mahimmanci.
"Binciken da aka yi na nazarin 70 ya nuna cewa hanyoyin da aka kafa al'umma sun yi tasiri wajen kara wanke hannu a cikin LMICs, yayin da kamfen na talla na zamantakewa ya yi tasiri. Misali na inganta wanke hannu a makarantu shine ""Tsarin taurari uku"" na UNICEF wanda ke karfafa makarantun su dauki matakai masu sauki da kuma saukin kudi, kamar tabbatar da cewa ban da bin sauran bukatun kiwon lafiya, dalibai suna wanke hannayensu da sabulu. "
Bayan samun mafi ƙarancin ƙimar, makarantu na iya samun ci gaba daga tauraro ɗaya zuwa ƙarshe zuwa tauraro uku.
Gina tashoshin wanke hannu na iya zama wani ɓangare na kamfen na talla na wanke hannu wanda ke da nufin rage cututtukan yara da mutuwar yara.
Ranar Wanke Hannun Duniya wani misali ne na kamfen wayar da kan jama'a wanda ke kokarin canza halayyar. A yayin annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20, UNICEF ta inganta amfani da emojis na wanke hannu.
Karamin bincike ya yi la'akari da tasirin tasirin tasirin tsaftace hannu a cikin ƙasashe masu tasowa dangane da DALYs.
Koyaya, wani bincike ya nuna cewa inganta wanke hannu da sabulu ya fi sauran hanyoyin ruwa da tsaftacewa tsada.
"Mahimmancin wanke hannu ga lafiyar ɗan adam musamman ga mutane masu rauni kamar uwaye da suka haihu ko sojoji da suka ji rauni a asibitoci an fara gabatar da su ne a tsakiyar karni na 19 ta hanyar manyan malamai biyu na tsabtar hannu: Likita Ignaz Semmelweis na Hungary wanda ke aiki a Vienna a Austria da Florence Nightingale, ""mai kafa cibiyar kula da lafiya ta zamani"" a Ingila. "
A lokacin, yawancin mutane sun yi imanin cewa cututtukan cututtuka sun samo asali ne daga ƙanshin da ake kira miasmas.
A cikin shekarun 1980, yaduwar cututtukan da ke yaduwa ta hanyar abinci da cututtukan da ke da alaƙa da kiwon lafiya ya sa Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka na Amurka suka inganta tsabtace hannu a matsayin hanya mai mahimmanci don hana fara kamuwa da cuta.
Barkewar mura ta alade a shekarar 2009 da kuma annobar COVID-19 ta duniya a shekarar 2020 sun wayar da kan kasashe da dama game da muhimmancin wanke hannu wajen hana irin wannan kamuwa da cuta.
"Misali, an sanya hotunan hoto tare da rubutun ""daidaitaccen hanyoyin wanke hannu"" kusa da wanka a cikin wuraren wanka na jama'a da kuma a cikin gidan wanka na gine-ginen gwamnati da filayen jirgin saman Jamus. "
"Farin cikin ""yanke mutum daga"" wani abu, yana nufin sanar da rashin son ɗaukar nauyi ko shiga ciki. "
Ya samo asali ne daga wani sashi na Linjilar Matiyu inda Pontius Bilatus ya yanke shawarar gicciye Yesu Kristi, amma ya sami ƙarin amfani a wasu maganganun Ingilishi.
"A cikin Shakespeare ""McBeth"", Lady Macbeth ta sake yin amfani da hannayenta ba tare da saninta ba don share ƙazanta, wanda ke nuna lamirinta game da laifin da ta aikata wanda ya sa mijinta ya aikata laifin. ""
An kuma nuna cewa mutane suna wanke hannayensu fiye da sauran mutane bayan tunatarwa ko tunanin ayyukan lalata kuma suna mai da hankali kan kayan wanka da wanke hannu.
Bugu da ƙari, mutanen da aka ba su izinin wanke hannayensu bayan irin wannan kulawa ba su da wataƙila su shiga cikin sauran ayyukan tilasta yin "tsabtacewa", kamar ba da kai.
Addinai suna ba da shawarar wanke hannu don dalilai na tsabta da alama. Wanke hannu na alama, amfani da ruwa ba tare da sabulu ba don wanke hannu, wani ɓangare ne na wanke hannu na al'ada wanda aka nuna a cikin addinai da yawa, gami da Baha'i, Hindu, Taoism da Nitiyat na Yama a cikin Yahudanci, Lawubu a cikin Kiristanci da Wazo a cikin Musulunci. Addinai suna ba da shawarar wanke hannu da kyau, musamman bayan wasu ayyuka.
Addinin Hindu, Yahudanci da Musulunci sun bada shawarar wanke hannu bayan wanka.
Addinin Hindu, Buddha, Sikh, Yahudanci da Musulunci sun bada umarnin wanke hannu kafin da bayan kowane abinci.
Kula da haɗarin aiki don COVID-19
Gudanar da haɗarin aiki don COVID-19 yana nufin amfani da hanyoyin kiwon lafiya da aminci don sarrafa haɗari da hana barkewar cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kula da haɗarin da ya dace a wurin aiki ya dogara da yanayin aiki da aikin da aka ɗauka kuma ya bambanta dangane da kimanta haɗarin tushen haɗuwa da cutar, tsananin cutar a cikin al'umma da abubuwan haɗarin kowane ma'aikaci wanda zai iya zama mai saukin kamuwa da COVID-19.
Bisa ga sanarwar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Tsaro ta Amurka (OSHA), ayyukan da ke da ƙananan haɗari suna da mafi ƙarancin haɗuwa da jama'a da sauran ma'aikata, ana ba da shawarar waɗannan ayyukan su ɗauki mafi ƙarancin matakan hana kamuwa da cuta, gami da wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan sun kamu da cuta, amfani da abin rufe fuska da tsabtace gida da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki.
Ciki har da ayyukan da ke da matsakaicin haɗari waɗanda ba sa buƙatar haɗuwa da yawa ko kusa da waɗanda ake zargi ko waɗanda ke da COVID-19, amma suna iya haɗuwa saboda haɗuwa kai tsaye da jama'a ko tafiya ta ƙasa da ƙasa.
Wannan ya hada da ma'aikata da ke hulɗa da jama'a a wurare kamar makarantu, wuraren aiki da ke da yawan jama'a da kuma wasu manyan shagunan sayar da kayayyaki.
Kula da haɗarin ga wannan rukunin, ban da matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta na farko, ya haɗa da iska ta amfani da matattarar iska mai inganci, kariya daga tari da samun damar kayan kariya na mutum don fuskantar mutumin da ke da COVID-19.
OSHA ta ɗauki ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da ke fuskantar hulɗa da mutanen da ake zargi da COVID-19 a matsayin masu haɗari a cikin ayyukan da ke da haɗari, wanda ya fi haɗari idan aka yi amfani da hanyoyin samar da iska ko ɗaukar samfura daga waɗanda ake zargi ko waɗanda ke da COVID-19.
Ya hada da kulawar hadarin aiki da ya dace da waɗannan ma'aikata, kamar su kulawar injiniya kamar ɗakunan iska mai matsin lamba da kayan kariya na mutum wanda ya dace da aikin.
Cutar COVID-19 na iya haifar da tasiri mai yawa a wuraren aiki.
Ma'aikata na iya zama a wurin aiki saboda rashin lafiya, bukatar kula da wasu, ko tsoron kamuwa da cutar.
Hanyoyin kasuwanci na iya canzawa, duka dangane da kayayyakin da ake buƙata da kuma hanyar samun waɗannan kayayyaki (kamar sayayya a cikin lokutan hutu ko ta hanyar isar da wuri ko sabis na hawa).
A ƙarshe, jigilar kayayyaki daga yankunan da COVID-19 ya yi tasiri sosai na iya zama matsala. Za a iya amfani da shirin shiri da amsa cutar mai yaduwa don jagorantar matakan kariya.
A cikin tsare-tsaren, ana la'akari da matakan haɗarin da ke tattare da wurare daban-daban na aiki da ayyukan aiki, gami da tushen haɗuwa da cuta, abubuwan haɗarin zamantakewa da na gida da abubuwan haɗarin kowane ma'aikaci daban, gami da rashin lafiya ko kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani.
Hakanan za a bayyana hanyoyin da suka dace na sarrafawa don hana waɗannan haɗarin da kuma wasu tsare-tsaren don yanayin da zai iya faruwa bayan barkewar cutar.
Shirye-shiryen cututtuka da amsawa na cututtuka na iya aiwatar da su ta hanyar la'akari da shawarwarin ƙasa ko na gida.
Manufofin magance barkewar cutar sun hada da rage yaduwar cutar tsakanin ma'aikata, kare mutanen da ke da babban hadari daga cututtukan da ke tattare da ita, kiyaye ayyukan kasuwanci da rage tasirin da ba daidai ba ga sauran kamfanoni a cikin sarkar samar da kayayyaki.
Matsayin cutar a cikin al'umma, inda kasuwancin ke, yana shafar amsoshin da aka karɓa.
Tsarin kula da haɗari tsari ne da aka yi amfani da shi sosai don kiyaye lafiya da aminci a wurin aiki don rarraba kula da haɗari bisa ga tasirin tasirin.
Inda ba zai yiwu a kawar da haɗarin COVID-19 ba, sarrafa injiniya sannan sarrafawar hukuma da ƙarshe kayan kariya na mutum sune mafi ingantattun hanyoyin sarrafawa.
Gudanar da injiniya shine cire ma'aikata daga haɗarin aiki ba tare da dogaro da halayyar ma'aikaci ba, wanda zai iya zama mafi kyawun mafita.
Kulawar gudanarwa shine canje-canje da aka bayar a cikin manufofin aiki ko hanyoyin aiki kuma ma'aikata ko ma'aikata zasu bi su.
Kayan kariya na mutum (PPE) ba su da tasiri sosai a kan sarrafawa da sarrafa injiniya amma suna iya hana wasu haɗari.
Duk nau'ikan PPE dole ne a zaɓi bisa ga haɗarin da suke da shi ga ma'aikata, a girka su yadda ya kamata (misali abin rufe fuska na likita), a yi amfani da su akai-akai, a bincika su, a gyara su, a maye gurbin su, kuma a buɗe su, a tsabtace su, a sake girka su idan ya cancanta, ko a jefa su don hana kamuwa da cuta.
Dangane da sanarwar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Tsaro ta Amurka (OSHA), ayyukan da ke da ƙarancin haɗari sune waɗanda ke da ƙarancin hulɗa da jama'a ko sauran abokan aiki.
Hanyoyin kariya na kamuwa da cuta da aka ba da shawarar ga mutane a duk wuraren aiki sun haɗa da wanke hannu akai-akai, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su kasance a gida idan sun kamu da cuta, amfani da abin rufe fuska, da rufe baki lokacin da suke tari ko tari, samun damar takarda da kwandon shara, shirya don sadarwa ta nesa ko lokutan aiki marasa tsari idan ya cancanta, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su yi amfani da sauran kayan aiki da kuma samun jadawalin tsabtace aiki na yau da kullun.
Ganowa da warewar mutane da ke iya kamuwa da cutar da sauri yana daya daga cikin muhimman matakai wajen kare ma'aikata, abokan ciniki, abokan ciniki da sauran mutane a wurin aiki.
Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Amurka (CDC) sun ba da shawarar ma'aikata da ke da alamun cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani su zauna a gida har sai zazzabi, alamun zazzabi, da duk wasu alamun sun shuɗe, aƙalla awanni 24 bayan dakatar da shan maganin zazzabi ko mai sauya alamun cutar, da kuma samar da ƙa'idodin izinin magani masu sassauci don ba ma'aikata damar zama a gida don kula da dangin da ke fama da cutar, kuma duk ma'aikata sun san sabbin ƙa'idodin.
Bisa ga sanarwar OSHA, ayyukan da ke da matsakaicin haɗari sun haɗa da ayyukan da ke buƙatar haɗuwa da yawa da kuma nesa da wasu a cikin ƙafa shida (1.8 m) kuma ba a san ko masu amfani suna da cutar COVID-19 ba, amma suna iya kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 saboda yawan shiga cikin al'umma ko tafiya ta ƙasa zuwa wurin da cutar ta COVID-19 ta ɓarke.
Wannan ya hada da ma'aikatan da ke hulɗa da jama'a, kamar waɗanda ke aiki a makarantu, wuraren aiki masu cunkoso da wasu manyan wuraren sayar da kayayyaki. Gudanar da aikin injiniya ga wannan rukunin da kuma rukunin da ke da mafi yawan haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin COVID-19, haɗakar da matakan haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin COVID-19, haɗakar da matakan haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin COVID-19, haɗakar da matakan haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗar